A bit of a problem has
occurred, mo.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
A merchant ship on its way to Goldmund
has run aground, mo.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
The guild has already recovered the
Divine Beast ship, but...

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It's broken in various places and is
no longer usable, mo.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
The maintenance crew is busy with another
merchant ship and we're short-staffed,
so we're in a bind, mo.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0006
rows.name:
As expected, you're so reliable, mo!
I'm counting on you, mo!
